@raise_poor_tax
title: Increase taxes on the poor.
subtitle: The NEF will feel betrayed...
choose-if: poor_tax_raise <= 5
unavailable-subtitle: The poor have no more to give.
on-arrival: poor_tax_raise += 1; poor_tax_lower -= 1; poor_tax_income += 2; nef_dissent += 20; economic_slowdown_points += 1

While raising taxes on the poorest may raise the most revenue it also results in a decline in economic activity, and reduces the governments legitamacy in the eyes of the working poor.

@lower_poor_tax
title: Lower taxes on the poor.
subtitle: The NEF is satisfied...
choose-if: poor_tax_lower <= 5
unavailable-subtitle: The poor already pay no tax.
on-arrival: poor_tax_raise -= 1; poor_tax_lower += 1; poor_tax_income -= 2; nef_dissent -= 10

Reducing taxes on the poorest Sahellan means a significant loss in revenue, however the extra money in pockets not only increases economic activity but also apporval of the current government.

